  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK308">
<l>iṇareri tōyvaṉṉa viṉṉā ceyiṉum</l>
<l>puṇariṉ vekuḷāmai naṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though one commit things against you as painful (to bear) as if a bundle of fire had been thrust upon you, it will be well, to refrain, if possible, from anger.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
